"""
# GC Async UDP I/O

GC async UDP is a compatibility facade over the no-GC backend libraries.
The synchronous datagram socket comes from `nogc_sync_mut`; the async socket
comes from `nogc_async_mut`.

Keeping this module as a facade prevents the GC library family from declaring
its own UDP runtime hooks. Platform-specific UDP behavior belongs below the
no-GC backend boundary.
"""

export use std.nogc_sync_mut.io.udp.{UdpSocket}
export use std.nogc_async_mut.io.udp.{AsyncUdpSocket}
